        <mxCell id="4tNV-_hVSo1LlsSkCFnZ-36" parent="1" style="text;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;" value="&lt;h3 style=&quot;font: 700 20px / 30px quote-cjk-patch, Inter, system-ui, -apple-system, &amp;quot;system-ui&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Segoe UI&amp;quot;, Roboto, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, &amp;quot;Open Sans&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, sans-serif; margin: 32px 0px 16px; color: rgb(249, 250, 251); letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(21, 21, 23); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;&quot;&gt;&lt;code style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; font-language-override: inherit; font-family: Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, &amp;quot;Cascadia Mono&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Ubuntu Mono&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;DejaVu Sans Mono&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Liberation Mono&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;JetBrains Mono&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Fira Code&amp;quot;, Cousine, &amp;quot;Roboto Mono&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Courier New&amp;quot;, Courier, sans-serif, system-ui; background-color: rgb(44, 44, 46); border-radius: 6px; align-items: center; padding: 0px 5px; display: inline-flex; font-size: inherit;&quot;&gt;ggml_backend_buffer_i&lt;/code&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;(缓冲区实例接口)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;ds-markdown-paragraph&quot; style=&quot;margin: 16px 0px; color: rgb(249, 250, 251); font-family: quote-cjk-patch, Inter, system-ui, -apple-system, &amp;quot;system-ui&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Segoe UI&amp;quot;, Roboto, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, &amp;quot;Open Sans&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(21, 21, 23); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;&quot;&gt;它定义了&lt;/span&gt;&lt;strong style=&quot;font-weight: 600;&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;&quot;&gt;如何操作&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;&quot;&gt;一块已经被分配好的具体内存。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul style=&quot;margin: 16px 0px; padding-left: 18px; color: rgb(249, 250, 251); font-family: quote-cjk-patch, Inter, system-ui, -apple-system, &amp;quot;system-ui&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Segoe UI&amp;quot;, Roboto, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, &amp;quot;Open Sans&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(21, 21, 23); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;&quot;&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;ds-markdown-paragraph&quot; style=&quot;margin-top: 0px !important; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong style=&quot;font-weight: 600;&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;&quot;&gt;作用&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;&quot;&gt;：它代表了一块实实在在的内存区域（大小已知，地址已知）。所有对这块内存的读写、拷贝、清零等操作都由它的方法完成。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li style=&quot;margin-top: 6px;&quot;&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;ds-markdown-paragraph&quot; style=&quot;margin-top: 0px !important; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong style=&quot;font-weight: 600;&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;&quot;&gt;生命周期&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;&quot;&gt;：由&lt;span&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;code style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; font-stretch: 100%; line-height: 22px; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-size-adjust: none; font-kerning: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-language-override: normal; font-family: Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, &amp;quot;Cascadia Mono&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Ubuntu Mono&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;DejaVu Sans Mono&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Liberation Mono&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;JetBrains Mono&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Fira Code&amp;quot;, Cousine, &amp;quot;Roboto Mono&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Courier New&amp;quot;, Courier, sans-serif, system-ui; background-color: rgb(44, 44, 46); border-radius: 6px; align-items: center; padding: 0px 5px; display: inline-flex; font-size: 0.875em !important;&quot;&gt;buffer_type_i&lt;/code&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;的&lt;span&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;code style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; font-stretch: 100%; line-height: 22px; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-size-adjust: none; font-kerning: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-language-override: normal; font-family: Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, &amp;quot;Cascadia Mono&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Ubuntu Mono&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;DejaVu Sans Mono&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Liberation Mono&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;JetBrains Mono&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Fira Code&amp;quot;, Cousine, &amp;quot;Roboto Mono&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Courier New&amp;quot;, Courier, sans-serif, system-ui; background-color: rgb(44, 44, 46); border-radius: 6px; align-items: center; padding: 0px 5px; display: inline-flex; font-size: 0.875em !important;&quot;&gt;alloc_buffer&lt;/code&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;创建，并由其&lt;span&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;code style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; font-stretch: 100%; line-height: 22px; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-size-adjust: none; font-kerning: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-language-override: normal; font-family: Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, &amp;quot;Cascadia Mono&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Ubuntu Mono&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;DejaVu Sans Mono&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Liberation Mono&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;JetBrains Mono&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Fira Code&amp;quot;, Cousine, &amp;quot;Roboto Mono&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Courier New&amp;quot;, Courier, sans-serif, system-ui; background-color: rgb(44, 44, 46); border-radius: 6px; align-items: center; padding: 0px 5px; display: inline-flex; font-size: 0.875em !important;&quot;&gt;free_buffer&lt;/code&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;销毁。每个具体的分配都会产生一个新的实例。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li style=&quot;margin-top: 6px;&quot;&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;ds-markdown-paragraph&quot; style=&quot;margin-top: 0px !important; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 8px; margin-left: 0px;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong style=&quot;font-weight: 600;&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;&quot;&gt;核心方法&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;&quot;&gt;：&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul style=&quot;margin: 4px 0px 0px; padding-left: 18px;&quot;&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;ds-markdown-paragraph&quot; style=&quot;margin-top: 0px !important; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px;&quot;&gt;&lt;code style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; font-stretch: 100%; line-height: 22px; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-size-adjust: none; font-kerning: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-language-override: normal; font-family: Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, &amp;quot;Cascadia Mono&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Ubuntu Mono&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;DejaVu Sans Mono&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Liberation Mono&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;JetBrains Mono&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Fira Code&amp;quot;, Cousine, &amp;quot;Roboto Mono&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Courier New&amp;quot;, Courier, sans-serif, system-ui; background-color: rgb(44, 44, 46); border-radius: 6px; align-items: center; padding: 0px 5px; display: inline-flex; font-size: 0.875em !important;&quot;&gt;get_base&lt;/code&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;&quot;&gt;：获取这块内存的起始指针。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li style=&quot;margin-top: 6px;&quot;&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;ds-markdown-paragraph&quot; style=&quot;margin-top: 0px !important; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px;&quot;&gt;&lt;code style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; font-stretch: 100%; line-height: 22px; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-size-adjust: none; font-kerning: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-language-override: normal; font-family: Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, &amp;quot;Cascadia Mono&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Ubuntu Mono&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;DejaVu Sans Mono&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Liberation Mono&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;JetBrains Mono&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Fira Code&amp;quot;, Cousine, &amp;quot;Roboto Mono&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Courier New&amp;quot;, Courier, sans-serif, system-ui; background-color: rgb(44, 44, 46); border-radius: 6px; align-items: center; padding: 0px 5px; display: inline-flex; font-size: 0.875em !important;&quot;&gt;set_tensor&lt;/code&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;/&lt;span&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;code style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; font-stretch: 100%; line-height: 22px; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-size-adjust: none; font-kerning: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-language-override: normal; font-family: Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, &amp;quot;Cascadia Mono&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Ubuntu Mono&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;DejaVu Sans Mono&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Liberation Mono&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;JetBrains Mono&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Fira Code&amp;quot;, Cousine, &amp;quot;Roboto Mono&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Courier New&amp;quot;, Courier, sans-serif, system-ui; background-color: rgb(44, 44, 46); border-radius: 6px; align-items: center; padding: 0px 5px; display: inline-flex; font-size: 0.875em !important;&quot;&gt;get_tensor&lt;/code&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;&quot;&gt;：在宿主内存和该设备内存之间拷贝张量数据。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li style=&quot;margin-top: 6px;&quot;&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;ds-markdown-paragraph&quot; style=&quot;margin-top: 0px !important; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px;&quot;&gt;&lt;code style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; font-stretch: 100%; line-height: 22px; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-size-adjust: none; font-kerning: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-language-override: normal; font-family: Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, &amp;quot;Cascadia Mono&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Ubuntu Mono&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;DejaVu Sans Mono&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Liberation Mono&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;JetBrains Mono&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Fira Code&amp;quot;, Cousine, &amp;quot;Roboto Mono&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Courier New&amp;quot;, Courier, sans-serif, system-ui; background-color: rgb(44, 44, 46); border-radius: 6px; align-items: center; padding: 0px 5px; display: inline-flex; font-size: 0.875em !important;&quot;&gt;clear&lt;/code&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;&quot;&gt;：将整块内存置零或设为特定值。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li style=&quot;margin-top: 6px;&quot;&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;ds-markdown-paragraph&quot; style=&quot;margin-top: 0px !important; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px;&quot;&gt;&lt;code style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; font-stretch: 100%; line-height: 22px; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-size-adjust: none; font-kerning: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-language-override: normal; font-family: Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, &amp;quot;Cascadia Mono&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Ubuntu Mono&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;DejaVu Sans Mono&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Liberation Mono&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;JetBrains Mono&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Fira Code&amp;quot;, Cousine, &amp;quot;Roboto Mono&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Courier New&amp;quot;, Courier, sans-serif, system-ui; background-color: rgb(44, 44, 46); border-radius: 6px; align-items: center; padding: 0px 5px; display: inline-flex; font-size: 0.875em !important;&quot;&gt;cpy_tensor&lt;/code&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;&quot;&gt;：如果该缓冲区支持，直接拷贝张量（针对同类型设备优化）。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;" vertex="1">
